description:
Customize your drive with new Glade PlugIns Car. Simply plug the device into the nearest 12V outlet, turn on the ignition and transform any drive into an adventure for up to 60 days. Glade PlugIns Car only works when the car is running, and a glow indicates when the product is working.
Few scents are as iconic as the inviting smell of a new car. Let the subtle hints of bergamot, lavender and lemon in Glade New Car Feel keep your home-on-the-road smelling fresh for many miles to come.

DIRECTIONS FOR USE: Press down on front release tab to open lid. Pull tab to remove foil from refill. Place refill inside device with flat surface up, aligning the + and - symbols on the device and the refill. Close lid, pressing until you hear multiple audible clicks. Adjust switch to desired intensity level. Plug into the 12V outlet in your car. Turn on the ignition. A colored glow will light indicating that the unit is working.
Note: The device will switch off when the ignition is turned off to avoid waste. When the 12V outlet is not wired to the ignition the device will automatically shut-off after 30 minutes.

USES: Glade automotive air fresheners provide a known, trusted fragrance.
